OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening and overnight
OL,7,Fwith some evening sunshine. Skies
OL,8,Fbecoming increasingly cloudy through
OL,9,Fthe evening and overnight with odd
OL,10,Fspot of drizzle.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA largely cloudy start with
OL,13,Fpatchy rain. Slowly brightening up
OL,14,Fwith the best of the sunshine on the
OL,15,Fwest coast. Still warm but a bit less
OL,16,Fso than recent days.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,19,Fstart Sunday then brightening up with
OL,20,Fsunny intervals. Monday and Tuesday
OL,21,Fdry and sunny. Very warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
